Eileen Sedgwick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eileen_Sedgwick 0 Eileen Sedgwick (October 17, 1898 – March 15, 1991) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 115 films during her 15-year career. She was the sister of film director Edward Sedgwick.
